# SUPERVISOR
ADD supervisor_sshd.conf /etc/supervisor/conf.d/
ADD supervisor_unicorn.conf /etc/supervisor/conf.d/

# NGINX - Should be exporting /unicorn.sock to /var/run/unicorn.sock
ADD nginx.conf /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
ADD default_app.conf /etc/nginx/sites-available/default_app.conf
#RUN ln -sf /etc/nginx/sites-available/default_app.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/

# UNICORN
ADD unicorn.conf /etc/unicorn/unicorn.conf

USER deploy

# ADD APPLICATION
RUN git clone git@git.xogrp.com:Shared/taxonomy_api.git /webapp/current
WORKDIR /webapp/current
RUN git checkout master

USER root
RUN sudo /bin/bash -c "source /etc/profile && /usr/local/rvm/bin/rvm install `cat .ruby-version ` 2> /dev/null || rvm install 2.1.2"

# bundle install
RUN /bin/bash -l -c "bundle install"


CMD ["/usr/bin/supervisord",  "-c", "/etc/supervisor/supervisord.conf", "-n"]
